{"title":"Jupyter Notebook安装","slug":"Jupyter Notebook安装","date":"2021-02-25T23:58:00.000Z","updated":"2021-02-25T23:58:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Jupyter Notebook安装.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><h1 id=\"1-环境安装\"><a href=\"#1-环境安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 环境安装\"></a>1. 环境安装</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ sudo dnf install gcc gcc-c++ python3 vim</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ pip3 install --user -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple ipython jupyter notebook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"2-生成配置文件\"><a href=\"#2-生成配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 生成配置文件\"></a>2. 生成配置文件</h1><p>在用户目录运行以下命令，生成默认设置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ jupyter notebook --generate-config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>运行后会生成文件 <code>.jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py</code></p>\n<h1 id=\"3-登录密码\"><a href=\"#3-登录密码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 登录密码\"></a>3. 登录密码</h1><p>生成 jupyter notebook 登录密码文本（如果不配置登录密码，将难以登录和使用）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ python3</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> notebook.auth <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>passwd()</span><br><span class=\"line\">Enter password: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Verify password: </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">'sha1:df4a1......'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>exit()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在 <code>Enter password:</code> 后输入你想设置的登录密码。</li>\n<li>在 <code>Verify password:</code> 后再输入一遍刚才输入的密码。</li>\n<li><code>sha1:df4a1......</code> 是得到的加密文本</li>\n<li><code>exit()</code> 退出 python<h1 id=\"4-修改默认配置\"><a href=\"#4-修改默认配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 修改默认配置\"></a>4. 修改默认配置</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ vim ~/.jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight ini\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.ip</span>=<span class=\"string\">'*'</span> <span class=\"comment\">#设置所有ip皆可访问</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.password</span> = u<span class=\"string\">'sha1:df4a1....'</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 复制刚才生成的那个密文'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.open_browser</span> = <span class=\"literal\">False</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 禁止自动打开浏览器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.port</span>=<span class=\"number\">8888</span> <span class=\"comment\">#随便指定一个端口</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.notebook_dir</span>=<span class=\"string\">'/home/jupyter-notebook'</span> <span class=\"comment\">#启动文件夹</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"5-运行\"><a href=\"#5-运行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. 运行\"></a>5. 运行</h1>直接运行<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jupyter notebook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n守护进程模式运行<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nohup jupyter-notebook &gt; /home/hls/jupyter_nohup.out 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"6-配置多语言环境\"><a href=\"#6-配置多语言环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6. 配置多语言环境\"></a>6. 配置多语言环境</h1><h2 id=\"6-1-Java环境配置\"><a href=\"#6-1-Java环境配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.1 Java环境配置\"></a>6.1 Java环境配置</h2><h3 id=\"1-下载ijava\"><a href=\"#1-下载ijava\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 下载ijava\"></a>1. 下载<code>ijava</code></h3><p><a href=\"https://github.com/SpencerPark/IJava/releases\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/SpencerPark/IJava/releases</a> 或使用<code>wget</code>来下载</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir ijava</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> ijava</span><br><span class=\"line\">wget https://github.com/SpencerPark/IJava/releases/download/v1.3.0/ijava-1.3.0.zip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-安装\"><a href=\"#2-安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 安装\"></a>2. 安装</h3><p>先解压</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">unzip ijava-1.3.0.zip</span><br><span class=\"line\">python install.py --sys-prefix</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"3-查看\"><a href=\"#3-查看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 查看\"></a>3. 查看</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jupyter kernelspec list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"6-2-JavaScript环境配置\"><a href=\"#6-2-JavaScript环境配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.2 JavaScript环境配置\"></a>6.2 JavaScript环境配置</h2><p>需要有<code>npm</code>环境</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-下载安装\"><a href=\"#1-下载安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 下载安装\"></a>1. 下载安装</h3><p>npm会自动下载并安装</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g ijavascript</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-查看\"><a href=\"#2-查看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 查看\"></a>2. 查看</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jupyter kernelspec list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","more":"<h1 id=\"1-环境安装\"><a href=\"#1-环境安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 环境安装\"></a>1. 环境安装</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ sudo dnf install gcc gcc-c++ python3 vim</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ pip3 install --user -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple ipython jupyter notebook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"2-生成配置文件\"><a href=\"#2-生成配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 生成配置文件\"></a>2. 生成配置文件</h1><p>在用户目录运行以下命令，生成默认设置</p>\n<figure class=\"highl