\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.ip</span>=<span class=\"string\">'*'</span> <span class=\"comment\">#设置所有ip皆可访问</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.password</span> = u<span class=\"string\">'sha1:df4a1....'</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 复制刚才生成的那个密文'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.open_browser</span> = <span class=\"literal\">False</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 禁止自动打开浏览器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.port</span>=<span class=\"number\">8888</span> <span class=\"comment\">#随便指定一个端口</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">c.NotebookApp.notebook_dir</span>=<span class=\"string\">'/home/jupyter-notebook'</span> <span class=\"comment\">#启动文件夹</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"5-运行\"><a href=\"#5-运行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. 运行\"></a>5. 运行</h1>直接运行<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jupyter notebook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n守护进程模式运行<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nohup jupyter-notebook &gt; /home/hls/jupyter_nohup.out 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"6-配置多语言环境\"><a href=\"#6-配置多语言环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6. 配置多语言环境\"></a>6. 配置多语言环境</h1><h2 id=\"6-1-Java环境配置\"><a href=\"#6-1-Java环境配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.1 Java环境配置\"></a>6.1 Java环境配置</h2><h3 id=\"1-下载ijava\"><a href=\"#1-下载ijava\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 下载ijava\"></a>1. 下载<code>ijava</code></h3><